'From Squeak2.9alpha of 5 August 2000 [latest update: #3013] on 16 November 2000 at 2:49:28 pm'!"Change Set:		sysWindowRename-swDate:			16 November 2000Author:			Scott WallaceFor the first time attempts to establish a bridge between the titles of SystemWindows and object names as seen and changed in Halos.  An attempt is made to keep the two in synch."!!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'label' stamp: 'sw 11/7/2000 10:24'!externalName	"Answer the name by which the receiver is known in the UI"	^ labelString! !!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'label' stamp: 'sw 11/7/2000 10:26'!tryToRenameTo: aNewName	"Triggered eg by typing a new name in the halo"	self setLabel: aNewName! !